的歷史 <br />\n主角回到過去 遇上了MK妹 <br />\n仲中出埋條MK妹 <br />\n<br />\n之後MK妹大肚, 仲被殺害"},{"pid":"873e4db35edb6560ac2585791085f50f7a94f522","tid":1479401,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:58:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190815/s00001/1565881331334/警元朗檢7汽油彈-拘三人包括兩內地男\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565881331334%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%AA%A27%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75UwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=94f5c803\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565881331334%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%AA%A27%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7&h=a84c5bfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190815/s00001/1565881331334/警元朗檢7汽油彈-拘三人包括兩內地男</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190816/20750204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190816%2F20750204&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75UwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=1759525b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190816%2F20750204&h=c9f682e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190816/20750204</a><br />\n<br />\n車藏汽油彈　兩內地男被捕<br />\n2019-08-16<br />\n頭條<br />\n <br />\n元朗警署<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方昨凌晨在元朗路邊截查一輛可疑私家車，站在車旁的三名男子見狀逃跑但被擒獲，當中包括兩名內地男子。其間車上掉出一個紙箱，警員在箱內撿獲七個汽油彈，另一疑人則駕車逃去。警方正調查案件是否與近期連串示威活動中，警方被投擲汽油彈的事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n被捕三人包括兩名同姓李的男子（35歲及26歲），他們均為內地人；另一人則姓程（61歲），為本地人。三人涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途被捕。至於另一駕駛私家車的男子仍然在逃，警方正追緝該司機及私家車歸案。<br />\n<br />\n司機仍在逃<br />\n<br />\n現場是元朗青山公路屏山段往天水圍方向，昨凌晨1時許，警員巡邏時發現一輛形迹可疑的私家車停泊在上址，遂上前截查。涉案三名被捕男子當時站在車旁，他們見有警員隨即拔足向元朗市方向逃走，但終被警員擒獲。私家車司機則駕駛私家車往屯門方向逃去，其間車上掉出一個紙箱，警員發現紙箱內有七個汽油彈。事件中35歲姓李內地男子逃走時受傷，其後由救護員送院治療，案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎國剛"},{"pid":"c10c918fd1835a5ba817cd2594770b8c79bdca44","tid":1479401,"uid":276592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"575691224218d831f9939ecfb27687e5060a802f","tid":1479401,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:52:56.000Z","msg":"陳同佳引發第三次世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b8ad6e0689f099abe01386428657cf8a410a24","tid":1479401,"uid":89382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"係，就算777聽日話真點撤回都冇用，美國唔會就咁算數"},{"pid":"d428f0dfddcdfc7999204bb5cfd92099b07b0875","tid":1479401,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:01:34.000Z","msg":"仲有越南"},{"pid":"b834431d6aa2ab67fc0e184a65f483565d835ed5","tid":1479401,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:03:20.000Z","msg":"集中營-穆斯林"},{"pid":"73cc45c8113939568fbcbc4cd7c0ea99a5eb1389","tid":1479401,"uid":263336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbbd86eaf802b39df54995872d2392b6306a44a9","tid":1479401,"uid":3373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ff523f065c192e6be76900ec86035147423559d","tid":1479401,"uid":214036,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:42:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:44:38.000Z","msg":"諗諗下，中共隨咗朝鮮之外仲有啲咩盟友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":